OL,4,CMobile phone ban plan to improve school
OL,5,Cbehaviour
OL,6, Mobile phone bans and other ways to
OL,7, create "calm classrooms" are to be
OL,8, considered to help improve discipline
OL,9, in England's schools.
OL,11,FEducation Secretary Gavin Williamson
OL,12,Fsaid he wants to make the school day
OL,13,Fmobile-free, describing the devices as
OL,14,F"distracting" and "damaging".
OL,16,FA consultation will ask the views of
OL,17,Fteachers and parents on how to promote
OL,18,Fgood behaviour.
OL,20,FHeads accused Mr Williamson of being
OL,21,F"obsessed" with phones in school.
